REHEARING DOCKET

93-1887. Kokitka v. Ford Motor Co.

Cuyahoga County, No. 62410. Reported at 68 Ohio St.3d 1449, 626 N.E.2d 690. On motion for rehearing. Rehearing granted and motion and cross-motion to certify allowed; sua spante, cause consolidated with 93-2084, Kokitka v. Ford Motor Co., supra

Moyer, C.J., dissents.
